甜水海并无甜水，仅有一滩盐碱湖，生活用水及物资依赖外地运输。“甜水”一名源自该站曾经的一名老兵“想喝口甜水”的遗愿。<ref name="army">{{Cite web |title=甜水海兵站：孤单滋味苦变甜 |url=https://www.focusnews.net.cn/junshi/16416.html |access-date=2020-06-30 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804201910/https://www.focusnews.net.cn/junshi/16416.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=能在“甜水海”过夜，被高原上的兵视为骄傲 |url=http://www.sohu.com/a/239123791_119517 |accessdate=2021-02-19 |date=2018-07-03 |work=www.sohu.com |language=zh |archive-date=2020-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630043602/https://www.sohu.com/a/239123791_119517 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

